ce ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Beatrix De Wavrin was born as the daughter of Robert De Beaussart De Wavrin and Laure De Mauvoisin. She married Hugues De Melun about 1360, in Josselin, Morbihan, Brittany, France. They were the parents of at least 2 sons and 7 daughters. She died on 9 June 1419, in Antoing, Hainaut, Belgium, and was buried in Antoing, Hainaut, Belgium."},"et":{"–9 Jun 1419":"–9. juuni 1419","–1415":"–1415","–1419":"–1419","1330–1410":"1330–1410","1370–1421":"1370–1421","1370–Female":"1370–Surnud","1377–Female":"1377–Surnud","1405–1484":"1405–1484","1405–Female":"1405–Surnud","–1406":"–1406","–Female":"Surnud","1322–1398":"1322–1398","–1389":"–1389","9 Jun 1419":"9. juuni 1419","1484":"1484","1330":"1330","1370":"1370","1415":"1415","Abt 1377":"umbes 1377","1389":"1389","1410":"1410","1355":"1355","1322":"1322","1377":"1377","1421":"1421","1398":"1398","um 1360":"umbes 1360","1419":"1419","1406":"1406","1405":"1405","Melun, Seine-et-Marne, Île-de-France, France":"Melun, Seine-et-Marne, Prantsusmaa","Antoing, Arrondissement de Tournai, Hainaut, Belgium":"Antoing, Hainaut, Belgia","Josselin, Morbihan, Bretagne, France":"Josselin, Morbihan, Bretagne, Prantsusmaa","Josselin, Morbihan, Bretagne, Frankreich":"Josselin, Morbihan, Bretagne, Prantsusmaa","France":"Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"–9 Jun 1419":"–9. kesäkuuta 1419","–1415":"–1415","–1419":"–1419","1330–1410":"1330–1410","1370–1421":"1370–1421","1370–Female":"1370–Kuollut","1377–Female":"1377–Kuollut","1405–1484":"1405–1484","1405–Female":"1405–Kuollut","–1406":"–1406","–Female":"Kuollut","1322–1398":"1322–1398","–1389":"–1389","9 Jun 1419":"9. kesäkuuta 1419","1484":"1484","1330":"1330","1370":"1370","1415":"1415","Abt 1377":"noin 1377","1389":"1389","1410":"1410","1355":"1355","1322":"1322","1377":"1377","1421":"1421","1398":"1398","um 1360":"noin 1360","1419":"1419","1406":"1406","1405":"1405","Melun, Seine-et-Marne, Île-de-France, France":"Melun, Seine-et-Marne, Ranska","Antoing, Arrondissement de 